### Welcome to iCagenda GitHub Page.
There you will be able to edit the language files, and send me directly the info:


* [CZECH (cs-CZ)](https://github.com/JoomliC/iCagenda)
* DUTCH (nl-NL)
* ENGLISH (en-GB)
* FRENCH (fr-FR)
* GERMAN (de-DE)
* ITALIAN (it-IT)
* NORWEGIAN (nb-NO)
* PORTUGUESE / BRAZIL (pt-BR)
* RUSSIAN (ru-RU)
* SPANISH (es-ES)

Now, we have 10 languages available for iCagenda.

###
